- id: verify-playwriter-setup
  subject: Verify playwriter MCP is connected and accessible
  status: completed
  description: Confirm playwriter tool is available and working via MCP
  effort: small
  category: infra
  blockedBy: undefined
  acceptance:
    - Playwriter MCP connection verified
    - Can execute browser commands

- id: script-trends-navigation
  subject: Create playwriter script to navigate trends.google.com
  status: completed
  description: Use playwriter to visit trends.google.com and navigate to search queries
  effort: medium
  category: feature
  blockedBy: ["verify-playwriter-setup"]
  acceptance:
    - Script successfully navigates to trends.google.com
    - Can interact with search input

- id: extract-trends-data
  subject: Extract trends data from page DOM
  status: completed
  description: Use playwriter page.evaluate() to extract search trends, charts, related queries
  effort: medium
  category: feature
  blockedBy: ["script-trends-navigation"]
  acceptance:
    - Data extracted in structured format (JSON)
    - Includes search volume, time series, related terms

- id: create-cli-script
  subject: Create CLI wrapper script for trends queries
  status: completed
  description: Build executable CLI script (bash/node) that runs playwriter automation and outputs results
  effort: medium
  category: feature
  blockedBy: ["extract-trends-data"]
  acceptance:
    - CLI script executable
    - Accepts search query as argument
    - Outputs JSON or formatted results

- id: document-cli
  subject: Document CLI usage per playwriter README pattern
  status: completed
  description: Write setup and usage documentation matching playwriter conventions
  effort: small
  category: infra
  blockedBy: ["create-cli-script"]
  acceptance:
    - README explains usage
    - Example commands shown
    - Installation steps clear